{"tid":407452,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱係地鐵聽到個呀嬸話咩入會","createTime":"2017-09-20T12:26:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-20T13:40:31.000Z","uid":72812,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"abfd9285f335d16fd92a5bd49a192b9bf4d9ab7d","tid":407452,"uid":72812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T12:26:06.000Z","msg":"個呀嬸首先講咗堆唔關事嘅嘢，<br />\n話咩本身互聯網係美國嘅，<br />\n變左中國嘅之後就變左密聯網，<br />\n之後仲有70幾個國家支持佢咁做<br />\n<br />\n講到1999咁都唔知噏乜鳩<br />\n剩係聽得明話而家入會就唔洗錢，<br />\n仲送1000蚊中銀股票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇人知發生咩事<br />\n好驚家母中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3636f8fa8fe2cbaf861a129e07dab8c645b1e199","tid":407452,"uid":38970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T12:35:47.000Z","msg":"樓主已經比果個呀嬸既1999毒傳染左<br />\n唔想家母有事既就快啲睇醫生"},{"pid":"57bd9383f6698fd4a8fba12a73a7882c0c29ff43","tid":407452,"uid":72812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T13:40:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主已經比果個呀嬸既1999毒傳染左<br />\n唔想家母有事既就快啲睇醫生</blockquote><br />\n 咩呀 我真係聽到㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}